= ABOUT
This is GreaseMonkey "user script" (a.k.a. GreaseMonkey script) that will fetch the last entry on a FeedBurner feed and insert it to your Gmail Signature.

= REQUIREMENTS
  - In order to run you will need GreaseMonkey installed in your browser: http://userscripts.org/about/installing
  - A Feedburner feed, with the BuzzBoost option enabled (at the Publicize section) with the number of items to display set to 1.

= INSTALLATION and USAGE
 - You may install the script from http://userscripts.org/scripts/show/118317
 - Check http://userscripts.org/about/installing on how to install user scripts
